</taxonomicName>
occurs along the moist shady slopes near streams at an elevation between 
<quantity id="21249B799653FFAAFF4C471BF74FBF44" box="[237,365,1804,1831]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="8.5" metricValueMax="9.0" metricValueMin="8.0" pageId="1" pageNumber="262" unit="m" value="850.0" valueMax="900.0" valueMin="800.0">800–900 m</quantity>
along with 
<taxonomicName id="21DC4D1F9653FFAAFE54471AF50FBF45" authority="(Miq.) A. DC." authorityName="A. DC." baseAuthorityName="Miq." box="[501,813,1804,1831]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Begoniaceae" genus="Begonia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Cucurbitales" pageId="1" pageNumber="262" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="roxburghii">
<emphasis id="D4A8EA8E9653FFAAFE54471AF4A9BF45" box="[501,651,1804,1830]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="262">B. roxburghii</emphasis>
(Miq.) A.DC.
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="21DC4D1F9653FFAAFC98471BF6D5BF29" authority="Ram. Kumar, Sushil K. Singh &amp; S. Sharma" class="Liliopsida" family="Zingiberaceae" genus="Zingiber" kingdom="Plantae" order="Zingiberales" pageId="1" pageNumber="262" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="mizoramensis">
<emphasis id="D4A8EA8E9653FFAAFC98471BF21EBF45" box="[825,1084,1804,1830]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="262">Zingiber mizoramensis</emphasis>
Ram. Kumar, Sushil K.Singh &amp; S.Sharma
</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName id="21DC4D1F9653FFAAFE934727F7F5BF29" box="[306,471,1840,1866]" class="Lycopodiopsida" family="Selaginellaceae" genus="Selaginella" kingdom="Plantae" order="Selaginellales" pageId="1" pageNumber="262" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="undetermined">
<emphasis id="D4A8EA8E9653FFAAFE934727F7F5BF29" box="[306,471,1840,1866]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="262">Selaginella sp.</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="E663369C9653FFAAFF1C4743F726BFF1" blockId="1.[136,1452,796,2010]" pageId="1" pageNumber="262">
<emphasis id="D4A8EA8E9653FFAAFF1C4743F7C5BF0D" bold="true" box="[189,487,1876,1902]" pageId="1" pageNumber="262">Flowering &amp; fruiting:—</emphasis>
Flowering from last week of August to October and fruiting from late October to November.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
